{
  "stem": "18960.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 394.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They'll-- tonight, they'll recognize.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine how I felt every Saturday night?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I came for-- when my turn came there, I grabbed the end of my penis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I pulled a little bit the foreskin over it, and they looked, and-- and they never-- they never suspected me, and they went through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my heart was at my elbow every time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I figured this-- today will catch me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow, [INAUDIBLE] they never suspected me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I played my role so well, there was-- there was not a slight suspicion that I could be a Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is why they probably didn't pay attention to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was towards the end of April-- well, in '45, I would say it was March '45-- American airplanes were flying over our camp and throwing down these-- these metal strips and covering the whole camp with metal.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we didn't know the-- the meaning of these metal strips.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we knew these are Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was working at a kommando near Ravensbrück and from a-- from a high-- higher elevation, I could see Berlin.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not far from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you could see in broad daylight how American allied planes had been bombarding Berlin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a sight to see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We enjoyed tremendously-- we knew this is the end, that they were destroying the city of our-- of our-- where our torturers lived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we knew that the end of the war will come.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
